# Build context is the repo root; keep it lean and never ship secrets or local build output.
**/node_modules
**/target
client/build
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/*.iml
.fallow
.claude
.agents
# Secrets: the app gets config via env_file at runtime, not baked into images.
.env
**/.env
!.env.example
